Flow Nodes
Privacy Policy
We value your privacy and are committed to ensuring that your personal data is protected. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data in accordance with applicable privacy regulations, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
Data Collection
Flow Nodes collects limited data to improve the app experience. Specifically, we collect the following information:
The types of nodes that users create within the app.
The wired connections that users create between nodes.
It is important to note that
no personally identifiable data
is collected. The data we collect is used solely for improving the user experience and enhancing app functionality.
Additionally, we do not collect the following data:
We do not collect any image data.
We do not collect any video data.
We do not collect any face data.
We do not collect any audio data.
We do not collect any location data.
We do not collect any device data.
GDPR Compliance
As required by the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), we respect the following principles:
Data Minimization:
We only collect data that is necessary to improve the app, and we do not collect any personal information.
Lawfulness, Fairness, and Transparency:
We are fully transparent about our data practices and ensure that no personal data is processed unlawfully.
Rights of Data Subjects:
Since we do not collect personal data, there is no need for users to request data access, correction, or deletion.
Should our privacy practices change, we will update this policy accordingly and ensure full transparency regarding any data collection practices.
Last updated: 15th of February 2025